Well like, this has been very informative, I used to think that it was only the top and bottom rows that were invisible, but apparently the actionsafe region of the screen is two rows from the bottom/top edges, and one column from the left/right edge. Titlesafe would be 1 row/column inwards from those edges.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=21">Drag</a> — Fri Apr 29, 2011 10:35 pm</p><hr />
